OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAmerican XL bully          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsafeguards confirmed for   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FScotland                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, New restrictions on XL bully dogs are  
OL,6, being introduced in Scotland from 23   
OL,7, February.                              
OL,9,FIt will be legal to own one of the dogs
OL,10,Fbut they must be muzzled and on a lead 
OL,11,Fin public from that date. Selling or   
OL,12,Fexchanging them will be banned.        
OL,14,FAnd from 31 July it will be an offence 
OL,15,Fto own an XL Bully without an exemption
OL,16,Fcertificate.                           
OL,18,FThe regulations mirror those in England
OL,19,Fand Wales but certificates will be     
OL,20,Frequired there from Thursday.          
